{"tid":1133923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州醫院抽血不換針頭　醫生解釋：扎兩三個而已","createTime":"2019-05-01T12:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T13:04:23.000Z","uid":50769,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f42520e74a85d570e005914fb0bf51ca6c6585","tid":1133923,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"廣東省廣州市一家醫院的醫生為病患抽血時沒有換針頭，醫生還說：「應該沒有什麼，就扎了兩三個而已」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐上月11日帶孩子到廣州天河區人民醫院看病，抽血檢查後，她身後的另一名患者的家人無意間聽到兩位醫生對話。女醫生大聲問男醫生：「到底有沒有換針頭？」男醫生卻說，「這個應該沒有什麼，就扎了兩三個而已」。<br />\n<br />\n目前天河區衛生和計劃生育局已經介入調查，院生說，涉事的檢查科男醫生是實習醫生，已經離職，而陳小姐發現已要求重新為孩子抽血，希望未來3年內都能追蹤體檢，並堅持要求院方合理解釋。<br />\n<br />\n（廣東電視台）"},{"pid":"85fab3bac0a9273679ffb2c87bf0191bae7e0703","tid":1133923,"uid":194785,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:19:50.000Z","msg":"我黨支持環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n厲害了，我的蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836300e5ab12bd86ec1c85d16a2ceb6e65b10ebd","tid":1133923,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f80b3d34a122b49aeca20560d1b67040d42c5f06","tid":1133923,"uid":83732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"最緊要唔好比班大陸喱落到香港執業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff61e82a3b9062b736a21f2297126a803f8efa0f","tid":1133923,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d052c2a4e2403656f6549ea5ecc4736b7cb51b","tid":1133923,"uid":237733,"like":0,"dislike